成为一个不错的大人。 后来我升学了、工作了、结婚了、加入省作协了…但我好像很难真正地从青春期的伤痛中走出来，有个具体表现就是，我很难和自己的实际年龄和解，我经常幻想自己依然只有15岁，就在前不久，我还在幻想自己是个刚刚初中毕业的妙龄少女。 一来，我是真的比较留恋青春年华，哪怕青春里会有伤痛，可是十五六岁、十七八岁的岁数，本身就是美好的。 二来，我在15岁的伤痛中滞留太久了，因为走不出那一年的创伤，所以，我总是没办法面对自己不断增长的岁数，总是想治愈内心那个可怜兮兮的15岁豆蔻少女。 可就在今天晚上，我忽然决定好了，不会再幻想自己刚刚初中毕业什么的了，我以后要用自己的实际年龄去面对生活、面对世界，我不会再那么拧巴了… 现在，我已经27岁了，距离最伤最痛的那段光阴，已经整整12年了，我自我疗愈的速度会不会太慢了一点？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2bW4lcX70cwOEAMaCTEwODUyMDAwNiDBwvyyBjAAOCZADnIJNjU4MDg5MTY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6665e3f4f7efed25ca0c8b6be8a35957_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1718101083.902638","card_id":"Q_653491670","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":653491670,"title":"国内的骑行圣地都有哪些值得推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653491670","type":"question","created":1713563210,"answer_count":20,"follower_count":40,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[833,8879,97429,106407,3459087],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I2bW4lcX70cwOEAMaCTEwNzQ5ODI3MiDKzIuxBjAAOChAD3IJNjUzNDkxNjcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7f777e832e74bed99dc055075ac75142_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1718101083.902902","card_id":"Q_504314857","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":504314857,"title":"杭州有哪些地方可以一个人安安静静的待一天？","url":"https://api.zhihu